sources.description:
Divination (Dark Soul) - Supernatural forced collide when madness meets magic in “Divination”. Jason (D’angelo Midili) is a young, successful artist married to the lovely Jessica (Natasha Sims). They’re filled with joy at their first pregnancy and the uncanny return of their mysterious friend Dee (Lisa Coronado). But Jason is tormented by Fear (Tucker Boggio) continually whispering nightmares and horrific visions into his mind. As he descends deeper into madness an intervention is made by the powerful angel Joshua (Philipp Aurand), and his eager assistant Daniel (James Grixoni). “Divination” is pure spiritual warfare, a thriller like no other. Do not trust every spirit.
2011.  Stars: D'Angelo Midili, Natasha Sims, Lisa Coronado
